    <title>English</title>
    <link href="/2023/11/26/English/"/>
    <url>/2023/11/26/English/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="2023-11-26"><a href="#2023-11-26" class="headerlink" title="2023.11.26"></a>2023.11.26</h1><hr><h2 id="English-language-periodicals"><a href="#English-language-periodicals" class="headerlink" title="English-language periodicals"></a>English-language periodicals</h2><hr><h3 id="unfamiliar-words"><a href="#unfamiliar-words" class="headerlink" title="unfamiliar words"></a>unfamiliar words</h3><h4 id="Words"><a href="#Words" class="headerlink" title="(Words)"></a>(Words)</h4><p>1.concerted 一致的 <br>2.campaign 运动<br>3.literally 字面上<br>4.shed light on 帮忙弄清楚 ：<br>Two new studies shed light on the fact<br>5.vulnerable 更易受影响的<br>6.seek 过去式 (sought)<br>7.core 主要的<br>8.completed 已完成的<br>9.powerful marketing messages<br>10.implicitly 含蓄地<br>11.link A with B 将A和B链接到一起<br>12.prowess 杰出才能<br>13.masculinity 男子气概<br>14.bias 偏好<br>15.evaluative bias 评估偏好<br>16.cues 暗示<br>17.in this instance 在这种情况下<br>18.cognitive 认知能力的<br>19.cognitive process 认知过程<br>20.regulate our impulses 控制我们的冲动<br>21.tactics 手段<br>22.marketing tactics 商业手段<br>23.intangible 无形的<br>24.intangible benefits 无形效益<br>25.disadvantaged group 弱势群体<br>26.disadvantaged 弱势的，贫困的<br>27.constrained 拘谨的<br>28.skewed towards 有强烈倾向<br>29.nutritional 营养的<br>30.micro-nutrient 微量营养素<br>31.vitamin 维生素<br>32.mineral 矿物质<br>33.diabetes 糖尿病<br>34.oral 口腔的<br>35.kilojoules 千卡<br>36.satiety 饱足<br>37.scale 程度<br>38.satiety scale 饱足的程度<br>39.nutritionist 营养学家<br>40.cordials 果味甜饮品<br>41.adverse effect 有害效应<br>42.tax 税<br>43.place a tax on sweet drinks is one strategy(策略)<br>44.underlying 根本的<br>45.disgusting 令人反感的<br>46.via 通过<br>47.taste buds 味蕾<br>48.cordial 兴奋剂，补品<br>49.millennia 数千年<br>50.Human have quenched their thirst with water for millennia and that is what we need to get back to .<br>51.billboards 广告牌</p><hr><h4 id="Key"><a href="#Key" class="headerlink" title="(Key)"></a>(Key)</h4><p><img src="/images/pasted-0.png" alt="upload successful"><br><img src="/images/pasted-1.png" alt="upload successful"><br><img src="/images/pasted-2.png" alt="upload successful"><br><img src="/images/pasted-3.png" alt="upload successful"><br><img src="/images/pasted-4.png" alt="upload successful"><br><img src="/images/pasted-5.png" alt="upload successful"><br><img src="/images/pasted-6.png" alt="upload successful"><br><img src="/images/pasted-7.png" alt="upload successful"><br><img src="/images/pasted-8.png" alt="upload successful"></p><hr>]]></content>
    
    
    
