    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="How-to-use-Git-bash-to-revise-Github"><a href="#How-to-use-Git-bash-to-revise-Github" class="headerlink" title="How to use Git bash to revise Github:"></a>How to use Git bash to revise Github:</h2><h4 id="1-”Git-bash-here”-at-a-blank-file"><a href="#1-”Git-bash-here”-at-a-blank-file" class="headerlink" title="1.”Git bash here” at a  blank file"></a>1.”Git bash here” at a  blank file</h4><h4 id="2-If-you-want-to-clean-your-github-repositories"><a href="#2-If-you-want-to-clean-your-github-repositories" class="headerlink" title="2.If you want to clean your github repositories"></a>2.If you want to clean your github repositories</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ git <span class="hljs-built_in">clone</span> URL <span class="hljs-comment">#URL :find it in the code</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ git add .<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ git commit -m <span class="hljs-string">&quot;name&quot;</span> <span class="hljs-comment">#the name is not important,just for its need</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ git push <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="3-If-you-want-to-revise-your-blog"><a href="#3-If-you-want-to-revise-your-blog" class="headerlink" title="3.If you want to revise your blog"></a>3.If you want to revise your blog</h4><p> just clone and revise the file andthen follow steps like NO.2.</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
